description: You just feel nature when you get lost in it. Not forever, of course. But for a certain time when you feel free and independent. It gives us the frame to be creative and to try out new things.When we were on the Kermovan peninsula, we fell victim to the beauty of nature once again. We played around with the giant ferns, tried new stuff and had a wonderful time that we will definitely not forget. This is what nature does. It heals, it stays.
